## Quick Start

PSPDFKit is a mobile PDF SDK for iOS, macOS, Android, Windows, and Web that deals with everything related to PDF. It’s a large framework, and we expose a lot of API, so many aspects can be customized. The API can be intimidating at first, but you really only need the basics to [get started][Integrating PSPDFKit Android].

